products.title: Nile Taped Slate Grey With Contrast Dark Grey Tape Real Wood
products.description: Their nile contrast taped blinds come in several different tape and colour combinations perfect for any room in your home. This grey wooden blind has contrasting dark grey tapes which create a bold and quality finish. At swift direct blinds, we take quality seriously. With over fifty years experience in manufacturing and selling blinds in the uk, their wooden blinds are made by their expert team, and packed and shipped to your doorstep.
